Create and Share the Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking App

Available in: Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions where B2B Communications Cloud is enabled.

Navigate to CRM Analytics Studio. Click Create. Select App | Create App from Template, and then open the template picker. Select Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking, and then click Continue.

Review the app preview page. To open the configuration wizard, click Continue. If you're asked whether to base your app on an existing app or to create a new one, select Create a brand new app, and then click Continue.

Perform an action: Run a compatibility check against your org to ensure that the app contains the data required. Select the Service Order Management (SOM) dataset, created using external SOM data.

Enter a name for your app, and then click Create. After the process is completed, refresh the page. To share the app with users, open CRM Analytics Studio, select Give Access, and add user names under Invite others.

For each user, select their level of access: Viewer, Editor, or Manager. Save changes to share the app with your users.
title: Create and Share Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking App
